HEADWORD: Conject
<hw>Con*ject"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>conjectus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>conjicere</ets>. See
<er>Conjecture</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To throw together, or to
throw.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Bp. Montagu.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

